{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "7add2db0-32ad-433c-a7ec-848305e24f33",
    "name": "Science2-08-Science Friction Belt",
    "sceneId": "4c80661d-0537-46d4-b6d6-422313186fac",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "a6e64c0b-1421-4f17-9ec6-8834dab26829",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "dbd3a920-672d-41ac-9f35-390655ce447e",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "06d12076-11f5-40cb-adcb-89f8fa40d3f2",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I know many of you were rather shocked by yesterday's lecture at the notion that Magic and Science are not totally incompatible.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a952f264-33bb-4c9e-b57e-33aff157fdf4",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Many of you may think that Magic is like an acid and Science like a base, so that combining the two would have explosive results.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "136472cc-3209-45bf-b520-1b4565d8246c",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "However, in today's lesson, not only will you see Science and Magic combined, but you will have tangible proof that the two disciplines can be used to enhance one another!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e9ce06af-2380-4baf-932a-ffb2cffbe038",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We are going to create something those brainless imbeciles on Science Island allege is impossible - we are going to make Science Friction Belts!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b158534a-6780-4787-997d-cc3461cf5e55",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "These belts utilize the Magical runes of \"Protection\" and \"Defense\" and the amplifying principles of magnetism and metal. This generates a field of energy that surrounds the belt wearer and buffers against incoming physical damage.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "df803850-3b6d-420c-a312-f44dacf5046e",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The effect lasts for one hour of time before the metal heats to just below the burning point of skin, at which point the belt will not activate until the next day. It wouldn't be very much of a protection if it set the wearer on fire now, would it?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "dc34266e-7f5f-4306-971f-fe1b2771c408",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Now, are there any questions before we begin constructing this technical device?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "f68b67f2-748b-4cce-a619-ff082e8b9349",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6a2f44ca-68d5-49cf-bc97-4cbdf957693d",
                            "text": "Say Something Complimentary",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "08b19d68-5553-46d8-9a25-93106eed50a3",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "70",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "14086108-f797-407b-afbc-3f19ccda4bfa",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "eb5aaf4e-12f6-49bc-8f03-3b4afb710dd5",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Do you mean to say that you proved the people on Science Island wrong by combining Magic and Science? You'll go down in history!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "77352c11-687d-4983-b973-03bee0b154c9",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, well, I like to believe that my research will lead to a new field of study, <i>Magicology.</i> It will bring Magic out of the dark ages and Wizard towers into the futuristic laboratories of today!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f0bfdd94-20e7-4f1c-93bc-35de72d3aac1",
                            "text": "Ask About the Science Friction Belt",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "825472da-0c0c-496f-8e57-4d6db25f3da6",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "70",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "597076e9-afee-4275-aedd-f076f3a116f0",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1d397886-9823-4ab1-afdc-d92593c7f308",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So how does the Science Friction Belt actually work? Does it create a physical force field around someone?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "50a13abb-5743-4863-a880-b9f746860cf9",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The Science Friction Belt creates an energy field that uses the wearer's skin as a conductor to create a buffer of magic. This buffer resists the force of incoming actions, producting friction to slow down and reduce the damage.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dbbfee11-b542-4ade-a851-923e84100a6c",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It's very Scientific!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c494866c-6253-450c-913d-96ac8fc85cd5",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About Science Island",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "612fc90c-721f-4aef-a91e-f16089f82227",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "70",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "830726c8-32af-4aa6-947e-537534907190",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0f357b74-49dc-4cf5-b74a-17062a608f43",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So have you showed this belt to the fools on Science Island to rub their noses in their refusal to believe in Magic?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d422ea0d-8431-4d69-a328-4901340991b2",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Would you believe it? They refused to acknowledge that the Science Friction Belt's invisible protective field existed - Even when they could see it with their own eyes!",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "65e143b3-9b50-46cd-ad23-244aea073546",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So you say that this belt caused more friction between you and the Science guys? They couldn't see an invisible force field. Clearly they were blinded by the luddite!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "16a71c62-bedc-4f8a-b8f2-eee6b663244b",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "None is so blind as he who will not see the proof before his very eyes, even if it is invisible.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "7",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f9f1b43a-bdd9-413f-a044-d7103fea78cc",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0c4e3997-4742-44ee-8a1f-38a091b58505",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Very well, class, let's make your very own Science Friction Belt!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeInventory",
                    "id": "544876c2-658b-4fe6-9669-138d855ca7ec",
                    "propId": "cee8fe92-c08c-49ce-806c-c4b91599dca6",
                    "sceneId": "a2508b7e-a177-4a96-93bd-4d8ab88dffc4",
                    "change": "1",
                    "count": 1,
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "5f00e6df-8c23-443c-a5e6-aa96f3479559",
                    "name": "Science Friction Belt",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "Today in Science Lab, we made a belt that is supposed to protect me from incoming damage for one hour a day. Guess I'll have to remember to turn it on if I'm ever in danger."
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}